{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know what you are-- if you know what that means-- that [NON-ENGLISH], and things like that, important prayers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We said that some good things will come out of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sure enough, two days later, I go up and he has a map on the table put out, and he showed me that he can help me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I have to guarantee him with my life that nobody will escape, that everybody who he sent out will come back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because he is responsible for every one of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told him, I give you my guarantee with my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will not go till the last.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what had happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had to pick up all kind of merchandise, all kind of things for the buildings, for the roads, for the-- where had built bridges, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had to pick up all kind of things in one place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I could-- you know, like-- the camp was-- to make it [INAUDIBLE]-- the camp was right here, our city was here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had to pick up in between that note from our city, he had to pick up the merchandise.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he says, he can send the truck, you know, all around here, where it will go through our city, until-- to pick up and we go back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Five people can go on the truck, jump down, you know, in the beginning of the city, go to their houses, and a certain time to make exactly that time, there will be a safe place that the truck will come back to pick them up, back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And sure enough, that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
